{"nodes": [{"id": "home_michel_documentos_projects_hive_mind_cerebro_cortex_temporal_hive_mind_atoms_agent_loop_protocol_md", "label": "Agent-Loop-Protocol.md", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "cortex/temporal/Hive-Mind/atoms/Agent-Loop-Protocol.md", "source_location": "L1", "content": "---\ntags: [atom, loop, protocol, mandatory]\nstatus: active\ncreated: 2026-05-30\nupdated: 2026-05-30\n---\n\n# Agent Loop Protocol\n\nCiclo de execu\u00e7\u00e3o obrigat\u00f3rio de 6 etapas:\n\n1. **Analyze Events** \u2014 entender pedido + estado atual via session_search\n2. **Brain-First Lookup** \u2014 consultar vault antes de APIs externas\n3. **Select Tool** \u2014 UMA tool call por itera\u00e7\u00e3o\n4. **Observe & Verify** \u2014 No Fixes Without Root Cause\n5. **Iterate** \u2014 at\u00e9 conclus\u00e3o, sem batch completions\n6. **Submit Results** \u2014 entrega final\n\n## Regras de Ouro\n\n- **Boil the Lake**: implementa\u00e7\u00e3o completa, sem atalhos\n- **Evidence Before Claims**: testar antes de afirmar\n- **User Sovereignty**: Michel decide sempre\n- **No Slop**: s\u00f3 o resultado, sem enrola\u00e7\u00e3o\n- **File Integrity**: write_file/patch/MCP, nunca shell\n\nLinks: [[RESOLVER-Skill-Dispatcher]], [[Current State]]\n"}, {"id": "atoms_agent_loop_protocol_agent_loop_protocol", "label": "Agent Loop Protocol", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "cortex/temporal/Hive-Mind/atoms/Agent-Loop-Protocol.md", "source_location": "L8"}, {"id": "atoms_agent_loop_protocol_regras_de_ouro", "label": "Regras de Ouro", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "cortex/temporal/Hive-Mind/atoms/Agent-Loop-Protocol.md", "source_location": "L19"}], "edges": [{"source": "home_michel_documentos_projects_hive_mind_cerebro_cortex_temporal_hive_mind_atoms_agent_loop_protocol_md", "target": "atoms_agent_loop_protocol_agent_loop_protocol", "relation": "contains", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "source_file": "cortex/temporal/Hive-Mind/atoms/Agent-Loop-Protocol.md", "source_locatio